🤖 Multi-Agent System
Instead of one AI, Jarvis A2 has multiple specialized agents:
Research Agent – Searches and summarizes information.
Coding Agent – Writes and reviews code.
Planning Agent – Creates study and project plans.
Automation Agent – Controls your computer.
Vision Agent – Processes images and video.
Memory Agent – Stores and retrieves long-term knowledge.
🛠️ Suggested Tech Stack
Language: Python
Backend: FastAPI
Frontend: React or Next.js
LLM: Ollama (local) or OpenAI API
Frameworks: LangChain, LangGraph
Speech: Whisper + Piper/Coqui TTS
Vision: OpenCV + YOLO
Automation: PyAutoGUI, Playwright
Vector Database: ChromaDB or FAISS
Database: PostgreSQL or SQLite
Deployment: Docker
